caption.p: The best 2D representation found of the interactions between beta-sitosterol with ( A) PDE4 enzyme (PDB ID: 4WCU), ( B) COX-2 enzyme (PDB ID: 6COX), ( C) potassium channel (PDB ID: 4UUJ), ( D) bromodomain of human BRD4 in complex with midazolam (PDB ID: 3U5K), ( E) serotonin transporter (PDB ID: 5I6X), and ( F) bromodomain of human BRD4 in complex with alprazolam (PDB ID: 3U5J).
